death squads that the attorney generals office says are run by 
drug traffickers 
drug traffickers are attacking party members in revenge for 
attempts by leftist guerrillas to kidnap and ransom traffickers and 
their families the attorney generals office has said 
meanwhile bombings by drug traffickers have become so frequent 
that they are largely played down or ignored by colombias 
newspapers 
